Network(A tiny observation of Flux of energy(FOE))
===============================================
Network is the invisible/visible paths/routs/roads..so on through which one transmit/consume the energy/information.
One use network it must produce/consume energy.The exchange of energy/information/object..so on tell the story of requirement.
It may or may not be necessary to use all the network surrounded of some object for its transformation.
It use only the necessary network(ie. energy) that it required for  its transformation.

There are many types of network natural/human made.

Natural network
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
These are the networks create and use by nature to maintain the order of lives/objects/wave/particles/creation/fermentation/plantation/separation/destruction/construction/transformation....so on.
Here nature supply energy from many sources to many destinations.In this network there are continuous transmission of energy flow in the form of waves. 
Every objects in nature is under transformation rapidly(streaming). This transformation need some input, environment ,temperature,air ,water,fire...so.on.

There are infinite network create,destroy and sustain every moment of time by nature automatically. And every network contain infinite type of waves transmit inside it.(like many vehicles travel on road).
Based on the requirement and capability of object, it receive waves for its transformation.
The body of lives not simply transform from child to young and next to old.It not only required the food,water,air..so on.. but also many types of invisible energy in the form of waves body receive every moment during its transformation.

Ex-
-Tree use the many waves for maintain its growth
like ...sun light,carbon dioxide,air,water,soil,moisture,atmospheric pressure,temperature...so on
-Leaf of tree it self use many waves to maintain the greenery in itself.

***Natural network maintain the order of transformation****

Artificial network(need of life/full fill the wises of life)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
These are the networks made/establish and use by human beings for balance of their peace/happiness/life/life style/wishes/society/country/rights/humanity/honesty/business/electricity....so on...ie the exchange of energy in any form.

The invention of this network happen when humans being feel the unbalance of their lives or to full fill the wishes of their lives.

