-Invention of roads/transport
-Invention of some medicine/bio-technology
-Invention of mobile, airways
..so on..

Network(create to full fill the wishes of lives)
--------------------------------
This network create by some technician/engineer/business man...so on.
The purpose of these network is for business/engagement of human being with objects/entertainment..so on
Ex-
